content: Family dinner just turned into a pitch strategy session. They're lowkey helping me figure out the AI's next move. It's like a focus group at home, kinda hilarious.

Just got some investor feedback. They want to see our AI handle some crazy market swings. Guess it's time for some serious stress tests.
Had a breakthrough today. Our AI now adapts to market changes on the fly, not just old news. It's like it's learning from every trade we make. Gotta show this off to our investors.
